title: 135. Q&AF: Getting Out Of Ruts, Avoiding Destructive Paths & Impacting Your Child's Health
itunes:title: 135. Q&AF: Getting Out Of Ruts, Avoiding Destructive Paths & Impacting Your Child's Health
description: Do you find yourself in a rut? On today's episode, Andy answers your questions of how you should deal with negative people in situations you have to be involved in, how to stop yourself from going down a destructive path and how you can motivate your child to take their health seriously.
